  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_4124f0f4320c4813bf03ad1b15ea972e">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Scrapbooks, campaign material, speeches, photographs, political buttons, and other material chronicling Heyman's political career, collected by his staff assistant June Keith and campaign manager Peter Ilchuk.  Also a copy of John Mikytuck's documentary about Heyman and the early AIDS crisis in Key West, "The Newcomer."</p>  </scopecontent>
